{"tid":1751744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏左係手足用血和命換番嚟，唔好忘記被捕的手足。","createTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:05:44.000Z","uid":329415,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"be344c6016d28b7a102a52a51c70ac40ec42f363","tid":1751744,"uid":329415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有理大的手足，笑唔出，只有眼淚。香港人永遠要記住呢幾個月流過的淚！記住幾多晚香港人徹夜不眠，一世都唔好忘記好多手足受傷失蹤被自殺。"},{"pid":"28c069124a05e1d983b3a858b2ac19e7116a937e","tid":1751744,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ab613935bb26ec1afa5d53ffee04edfae1764c94","tid":1751744,"uid":283686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然未嬴 <br />\n不過嬴左GA一定要記住係所有手足GA努力換番黎"},{"pid":"e703fe3099dca9be7dbb84fb7d9fcca5e0b53201","tid":1751744,"uid":154063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:04:02.000Z","msg":"香港人報仇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi